y Rotation'' | ref = {{Harvid|Hardian 2013, JKT48 Launches Heavy Rotation}} | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130219062207/http://music.okezone.com/read/2013/02/16/389/762695/jkt-48-luncurkan-heavy-rotation | archivedate = 19 February 2013 | df = dmy-all }}\n* {{Cite news | title = Ini Nama-nama Finalis JKT48 yang Akan Audisi ke Jepang | url = http://www.tribunnews.com/2012/10/07/ini-nama-nama-finalis-jkt48-yang-akan-audisi-ke-jepang | work = Tribun News | publisher = [[Kompas Gramedia Group]] | date = 7 October 2012 | accessdate = 8 February 2013 | language = Indonesian |trans-title=These Are the JKT48 Finalists Who Will Audition in Japan | ref = {{Harvid|Tribun 2012}}}}\n* {{Cite episode|title=Interview with Japanese Music Producer Yasushi Akimoto |accessdate=6 February 2013 |series=[[TalkAsia]] |network=[[CNN International Asia Pacific]] |date=12 January 2012 |url=http://www.cnnasiapacific.com/press/en/content/757/ |transcript=Transcript |transcripturl=http://edition.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/1201/13/ta.01.html |ref={{Harvid|TalkAsia 2012}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226172710/http://www.cnnasiapacific.com/press/en/content/757/ |archivedate=26 December 2012 }}\n* {{Cite news | title = JKT48 Belum Mampu Tarik Minat Kalangan Dewasa | url = http://www.halojepang.com/gayahidup-hiburan/6308-jkt48 | work = Halo Jepang! | publisher = Bina Komunika Asiatama | date = 27 December 2012 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121230055153/http://halojepang.com/gayahidup-hiburan/6308-jkt48 | archivedate = 30 December 2012 | accessdate = 3 November 2014 | language = Indonesian |trans-title=JKT48 Not Yet Able to Capture Interest of Adults | ref = {{Harvid|Halo Jepang! 2012, JKT48 Belum Mampu Tarik Minat Kalangan Dewasa}}}}\n* {{Cite news | last = Maruli | first = Aditia | title = JKT48 punya Theater JKT48 | url = http://www.antaranews.com/berita/331883/jkt48-punya-theater-jkt48 | publisher = [[Antara (news agency)